# Component Standards

## Framework
- Use Material UI (MUI) for all UI components
- Use TypeScript (.tsx) for all component files

## Naming
- Use PascalCase for component names
- Add 'Component' suffix to component files
- Example: `WeatherCardComponent.tsx`

## Structure
- Ensure full type safety
- Prefer composition over inheritance
- Follow accessibility rules:
  - Include alt text for images
  - Use valid anchor tags
  - Follow ARIA best practices

## Code Quality
- No console statements (warn only)
- No debugger statements
- Prefer const over let
- Use strict equality (===)
- No unused variables (prefix with _ if intentionally unused)
